   700	7 Limitations
   701	The credibility tiers and realization distribution are judgment priors with no literature calibration;
   702	the ordering is defensible, the levels are not measured, and the stance sweep is the honest bound
   703	on their influence. The QALY lens counts only health, so the estimate is a floor on total wellbeing,
   704	and the causes where Scott concentrates — education, mobility, equity — are precisely those
   705	whose main benefits the lens excludes. Credibility shrinks toward zero but never below it,
   706	so the model places no mass on harmful giving. Allocation splits each organization’s dollars
   707	equally across its focus areas and service locations; both are coarse, and the geography audit
   708	covers only the 50 largest “global”-listed organizations. Realization is one global draw, so it
   709	cannot vary by cause. Archetype anchors treat heterogeneous organizations as draws from
   710	one distribution. Within each cause, delivery regions are priced identically, so the geographic
   711	decomposition exposes assumptions rather than measuring regional differences. The undisclosed
   712	third of dollars is imputed from a fitted elasticity, not observed. The routed global-health bucket
   713	prices its unattributable and high-income-region dollars — roughly a fifth of the bucket — at
   714	low-and-middle-income anchors, an upward-bias channel. Several cost priors average over mixed
   715	null-and-positive evidence before the credibility discount applies, so the two-multiplier separation
   716	of doubts is imperfect at those boundaries. The Dirichlet allocation spread is a subjective prior;
   717	uncertainty from the elasticity fit, unmatched filings, the focus-area crosswalk, and the geography
   718	audit is not propagated. Allocation shares are derived in nominal dollars and applied to the
   719	real total; re-deriving in real dollars moves shares by hundredths of a percentage point. The
   720	geography audit’s scalar U.S. shares and regional decompositions were reconciled separately
   721	and can differ by fractions of a point per organization. Finally, several anchors rest on a small
   722	number of quasi-experimental papers whose external validity to Scott’s grantees is exactly what
   723	the realization factor is guessing at.
