   726	Measured in health, MacKenzie Scott’s $26 billion buys an estimated median of about 202,000
   727	quality-adjusted life-years — several times its cost under the government’s own regulatory
   728	valuation — and most of that estimated health comes from the twentieth of her dollars funding
   729	health and development delivered abroad. The number is a model output under stated priors,
