,"giftAreas":["17"],"gifts":[{"amount":13000000,"year":"2025"}],"locations":["us_midwest_nd","us_midwest_nd_spirit_lake_reservation"],"essays":[20251209]},{"name":"Aaniiih Nakoda College","link":"www.ancollege.edu\/","mission":"At Aaniiih Nakoda College we aim to provide quality post-secondary education for residents of the Fort Belknap Indian Reservation and surrounding communities. Our College promotes individual and community development by maintaining and revitalizing the Indigenous lifeways of the Aaniinen and Nakoda Tribes and by preparing students to succeed in American technological society.","giftAreas":["3","11","15","17","23"],"gifts":[{"amount":0,"year":"2025"}],"locations":["us_west_mt","us_west_mt_blaine_county","us_west_mt_fort_belknap_reservation"],"essays":[20251209]},{"name":"Red Lake Nation College","link":"www.rlnc.edu\/","mission":"We provide excellent higher education grounded in Ojibwe language, culture, and values. We inspire and build people up with academic skills, confidence, and Native pride so they can make positive change in the world with a strong Native perspective.","giftAreas":["3","11","14","17","30"],"gifts":[{"amount":7000000,"year":"2025"}],"locations":["us_midwest_mn_minneapolis","us_midwest_mn_red_lake_reservation","us_midwest_mn_st._paul"],"essays":[20251209]},{"name":"East Central University","link":"www.ecok.edu\/","mission":"To prepare students for tomorrow's world through a dynamic & diverse learning experience.","giftAreas":["17"],"gifts":[{"amount":17000000,"year":"2025"}],"locations":["us_south_ok","us_south_ok_ada"],"essays":[20251209]},{"name":"College of Menominee Nation","link":"www.menominee.edu\/","mission":"As a Land Grant institution chartered by the Menominee People, the College of Menominee Nation infuses learning with American Indian culture and prepares students for leadership, careers, and advanced studies in a multicultural world. The College commits to research, promotion, perpetuation, and nurturance of