The working-paper deferrals remain reasonable, but two simple manuscript inconsistencies still warrant minor revision: the stance sweep is still called an “honest bound” despite its caption saying it is not a bound, and the revised regional classification is contradicted in the limitations wording. I’m recording those precisely, along with the artifact-only items that remain.
